+# Architecture Research: sokoban
+
+> Research output вҖ” recommended architecture with rationale and alternatives.
+
+---
+
+## Recommendation
+**Layered module architecture with a pure functional reducer for game state** вҖ” keeps the simulation logic side-effect-free and trivially testable, while a thin imperative shell handles the canvas, input, persistence, and animation. For a 10-level single-developer game this is the simplest decomposition that preserves clear module boundaries and avoids both god-objects and framework overhead.
+
+## Architecture Overview
+
